2011-10-10T09:38:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/germany-france-to-undertake-hard-detailed-work-on-euro.html
Chancellor Angela Merkel ’s spokesman
Steffen Seibert said Germany and  France  will continue to hammer
out the “hard” details on measures to fight the euro region’s
sovereign debt crisis and are “aware of their responsibility in
this extremely difficult phase.”  He was speaking to reporters at a regular government press
conference in Berlin.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
